{"tid":2182462,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阻市民致哀 警濫控 拘人 搶花","createTime":"2020-08-31T10:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T11:06:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b019f86f98bb431a4237ac5973c7cb0853829d","tid":2182462,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/76CXFYNXQ5EPTOFCSZ6EPDGYOM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2F76CXFYNXQ5EPTOFCSZ6EPDGYOM%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0xSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=28f1ec7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2F76CXFYNXQ5EPTOFCSZ6EPDGYOM%2F&h=c94b2fa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/76CXFYNXQ5EPTOFCSZ6EPDGYOM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n阻市民致哀 警濫控 拘人 搶花<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pxPm45PA3Epr4qYxPhW7TPNp728=/1771x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NQWCUA2QGJF4LP26G6TVW5NATU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpxPm45PA3Epr4qYxPhW7TPNp728%3D%2F1771x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNQWCUA2QGJF4LP26G6TVW5NATU.jpg&h=e9454bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員無差別截查市民，更舉電筒照向拍攝情況的記者。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】 網民發起毋忘8.31行動，昨多人在旺角MOKO及朗豪坊商場聚集叫口號，晚上一批人士到太子港鐵站C1出口外紀念慘案，獻花鞠躬，但遭警方警告違反限聚令，並搶走站外鮮花，其後包圍在場七人，帶走一男一女。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「懇請」區議員停太子站獻花  警重兵監控8.31悼念<br />\n<br />\n8.31一周年前夕，傍晚起陸續有人士到太子港鐵站B1出口放置鮮花、食物及水致意，亦有人在鮮花包裝紙上寫上「深切哀悼831傷亡者」字句，惟旁邊的旺角警署有警員警告獻花。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「好難怪人話佢黑警」<br />\n<br />\n晚上有數十人在太子站外叫口號，約9時45分，站內一批警員衝出，約70名警員封鎖出口包圍七人，其中一名中年婦人及一名印巴裔人士被帶上警車，另至少一人被票控。<br />\n<br />\n悼念活動早於午間開始，有網民發起在旺角MOKO舉行毋忘8.31行動，警方高調戒備，在MOKO、朗豪坊和尖沙嘴海港城等商場外頻。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n數十名警員下午約3時半步入商場，在商場多處截停市民，並票控部份人。立場新聞引述被票控的張先生稱，他剛到商場，「警察就衝埋嚟，同佢講，佢唔信&hellip;&hellip;好難怪人話佢黑警」，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n人群其後「流水式」轉至朗豪坊， 大批警員近6時進入商場截查十多人，包括三名記者，其中被票控的網媒「馬聞」記者陳先生引述警員對他指，經「專家」驗證後，他和另外兩名網媒。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨大舉巡邏油尖旺區，大量年輕人被截查。其中在旺角港鐵站收費區，警方稱截查一名16歲男子，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eGJPFRc1_R1qGry3_zBUk0encGw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ET3H5NW7XFGDZD7I7CE47UZWJE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeGJPFRc1_R1qGry3_zBUk0encGw%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FET3H5NW7XFGDZD7I7CE47UZWJE.jpg&h=07a0c8dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大批警員闖入朗豪坊阻礙悼念活動，更舉槍指向上層市民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/828AGHM6iGfaWPO4dHnNYoRtW20=/1375x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6JL6M4ZJSZGZVMOXQ6DZTSCKFI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F828AGHM6iGfaWPO4dHnNYoRtW20%3D%2F1375x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6JL6M4ZJSZGZVMOXQ6DZTSCKFI.jpg&h=b250eac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有人手持《蘋果日報》參與紀念活動。"},{"pid":"6028ddb28d0955d788373eb02dce63719988adea","tid":2182462,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"冚家剷"},{"pid":"d0dca6479a7fef26c30ae14fa6dae21671dd7caf","tid":2182462,"uid":305602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2dt0hDKK130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2dt0hDKK130&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0xSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=050e0668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2dt0hDKK130</a>"}]}